    "product_details_gLrgBJ": {
      "type": "product-details",
      "blocks": {
        "description_w7TU9P": {
          "type": "description",
          "settings": {
            "description_heading": "Introduction"
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_PAyNwP": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Key Features",
            "content": "<ul><li>14 Driver Tri-Hybrid Architecture</li><li>4 Electrostatic Super Tweeter</li><li>Dual Diaphragm Isobaric Woofer</li><li>Super-Low Flat Impedance (SLFI)</li><li>5 Way Passive Crossover Design </li><li>48\" Null Audio Lune Premium Cable 4.4mm Balanced</li><li>2 Woofer | 2 Low-Range | 2 Mid-Range | 4 Mid-High | 4 EST Driver</li></ul>"
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_n38dzJ": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Quad Electrostatic Super Tweeter",
            "content": "<p>Powered by the cutting-edging miniature electrostatic tweeter technology, the driver employs a six-micro gram, gold plated membrane held against a plate charged up to 400 volts. The electrical signal voltage is amplified up to 100 times via a built-in miniature transformer. The electrostatic attraction and repulsion effects induced by music signal triggers the membrane to produce acoustic pressure. Simply plug into your player and high-fidelity music is ready to go.</p>"
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_fPHfQE": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Dual Isobaric Dynamic Woofer",
            "content": "<p>The Canary's 6mm dual isobaric woofer is designed for exceptional bass performance while maintaining overall audio balance. Featuring dual diaphragms and high-strength neodymium magnets, it delivers powerful and precise sound with minimal distortion. The isobaric configuration, where two drivers work in tandem, reduces Total Harmonic Distortion (THD) and enables deeper, cleaner bass. Advanced acoustic filtering ensures the woofer operates within a specific frequency range, minimizing overlap with balanced armature drivers for accurate and detailed sound reproduction. High-strength magnets enhance efficiency and responsiveness, providing fast transient response and detailed bass nuances. Together, these innovations create a rich, immersive listening experience with powerful, well-balanced bass seamlessly integrated into the overall sound signature.</p>"
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_HffCBq": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "3D Printed Enclosure and Precision Engineering",
            "content": "<p>The Canary Pro benefits from a wholly digitized design process that incorporates AAW's 3rd generation digital enclosure and acoustic chamber design. The enclosure and dynamic driver acoustic chamber are separately printed and assembled into a metal nozzle system. Extensive simulations are conducted to determine the ideal phasing and response for driver and nozzle placements. These simulations are performed hundreds of times to ensure optimal performance. The components are then 3D printed to precise tolerances, resulting in consistency in mass production. The advanced digital design process ensures that the Canary Pro delivers exceptional sound quality and a consistent listening experience.</p>"
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_XefaKL": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Accessories and Warranty",
            "content": "<p>48\" Null Audio Lune Cable 4.4mm Balanced </p><p>Genuine Leather Carry Case</p><p>Cleaning Tool</p><p>Owner's Club Card</p><p>3 Pairs SpinFit Silicone Tip(S/M/L)*<br/>3 Pairs AAW Short Stem Foam Tips(S/M/L)*<br/>6 Pairs AAW Assorted Silicone Tips (S/M/LX2)*<br/>1 Year Limited Warranty</p><p></p><p>* For Universal Fit Only</p>"
          }
        },
