          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/LUNE8_01_2048x_ed05a042-095c-4748-9ca3-cf5a46f1bd6f.webp",
            "heading": "Lune Premium Upgrade Cable",
            "heading_size": "h3",
            "seo_heading": "h3",
            "description": "<p>Crafted with precision, the Lune MKVIII features Null Audio's proprietary silver/copper fusion material, ensuring unmatched performance by reducing interference and eliminating unwanted noise.</p>"
          }
        },
        "image_RapkTH": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/CanaryProWeb01.jpg",
            "heading": "Exclusive Faceplate Design",
            "heading_size": "h3",
            "seo_heading": "h3",
            "description": "<p>The Canary Pro features a carefully curated faceplate design that utilizes nature pearl in conjunction with synthesized material. The two material is thoughtfully cut and placed by hand to offer a unique aesthetic appearance and complement the overall design of the earphones. Each piece of Canary Pro’s faceplate is absolutely one of a kind.</p>"
