          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Z06_SpinFit_2_7194d89f-916b-452d-8d36-87231288acd3.jpg",
            "heading": "Spinfit Eartips and More",
            "heading_size": "h3",
            "seo_heading": "h3",
            "description": "<p>The Canary ships with Spinfit eartips, as well as foam and silicone tips in various sizes and flexibility. This allows you to experiment with different tips to tailor the bass and treble sound signature to your preference, ensuring the perfect fit and personalized audio experience.</p><p><strong>* Custom Fit Monitor does NOT ship with any ear tips nor does it need them.</strong></p>"
