            "media_image": "shopify://shop_images/UIEM-FITTMENT_5f41ad49-86d2-4e8a-adeb-bc2045e79933.jpg",
            "column": 3,
            "row": 3,
            "column_mobile": "2",
            "row_mobile": "2",
            "heading": "IMPECCABLE UNIVERSAL FITMENT",
            "heading_size": "h5",
            "seo_heading": "h5",
            "description": "AAW leverages a vast database of thousands of ear impressions collected over the years to design universal-fit in-ear monitors (IEMs) that emulate the comfort and seal of custom-fit models. By analyzing ear anatomy patterns and using advanced 3D modeling and manufacturing techniques, AAW creates ergonomic shells that fit a wide range of ear shapes. Rigorous user testing ensures a secure fit, optimal comfort, and superior acoustic performance, delivering a near-custom experience for audiophiles and professionals alike.",
