            "description": "AAW's UIEMs and CIEMs are meticulously crafted using medical-grade resin or PVD aluminum, offering a dense, impact-resistant housing for exceptional durability. The skin-friendly resin is further enhanced with an anti-bacterial lacquer, ensuring added protection and irritation-free comfort.",
